<br>
1. I love going to a new world where I can be broke and have to earn every damn thing I get. (done this 3 times)<br>
2. If I can twink I do and enjoy doing it. (done many times)<br>
3. I would suport lvl limits on ALL equipment.<br>
<br>
Basically if I am on a world and start a new character there and do not twink it makes it feel fake to me, I am poor only because I choose to be poor. <br>
<br>
I love being on a new world where I can strive for that peice of armor etc but once I have options I take them.<br>
<br>
In my mind I try and keep RP sense for this, of course one of the most powerful twinking things is information, and lets face it, if yo uhave played as long as some of us have you cannot start out truly poor in the same way as the first time you played.<br>
<br>
Cheers to verant for the equipment lvl concept. I suppose if this carried on to the extreme it would make starting a new character more challenging and would totaly trash the market ;-) but I am still tempted by it :-)<br>
<br>
Wish I could be like Iris who resists twinking and has to be almost forced to except equipment from out of her scope for that character :-)<br>
<br>
Hugs to all<br>
